CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 3, 1966, pg. 13A, reads: "Daughters of Isis - When Sahara Court 9, Daughters of Isis entertained friends at their third annual Ball recently, the group honored two of their members. Held in ballroom of the Pick - Roosevelt Hotel... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of seven women wearing light colored gowns and fezzes, posed in Roosevelt Hotel for annual Daughters of Isis ball
